tc_game_paths.ext_script:
import clr from TCAdmin.SDK.Misc import CompressionTools from System import String from System.IO import Directory, File, Path from System.Net import WebClient from System.Diagnostics import Process from TCAdmin.SDK.Misc import CompressionTools
_7zaurl="https://www.7-zip.org/a/7za920.zip" _7zazip=Path.Combine(TCAdminFolder, "Monitor", "Tools", "7za.zip") _7zapath=Path.Combine(TCAdminFolder, "Monitor", "Tools", "7za") _7zaexe = Path.Combine(_7zapath, "7za.exe")
#Download 7zip if needed
if not File.Exists(_7zaexe) : Script.WriteToConsole("Downloading 7zip...") wc = WebClient() wc.DownloadFile(_7zaurl, _7zazip); c=CompressionTools() c.Decompress(_7zazip, _7zapath) File.Delete(_7zazip)
#Extract fivem.7z p = Process() p.StartInfo.FileName=_7zaexe p.StartInfo.Arguments=String.Format('x -y -o"{0}" "{1}"', FilesFolderFullName, DownloadedFile) p.StartInfo.WorkingDirectory=_7zapath p.Start() p.WaitForExit()
File.Delete(DownloadedFile)
#Download server-data
p = Process() p.StartInfo.FileName="git.exe" p.StartInfo.Arguments="clone https://github.com/citizenfx/cfx-server-data.git server-data" p.StartInfo.WorkingDirectory=FilesFolderFullName p.Start() p.WaitForExit()

tc_game_config_files.template:
set steam_webApiKey "![Steamkey]" # Enter your Steam API Key
# you probably don't want to change these! # only change them if you're using a server with multiple network interfaces endpoint_add_tcp "$[Service.IpAddress]:$[Service.GamePort]" endpoint_add_udp "$[Service.IpAddress]:$[Service.GamePort]"
start mapmanager start chat start spawnmanager start sessionmanager start fivem start hardcap start rconlog start scoreboard start playernames
sv_scriptHookAllowed 1
# change this rcon_password $[RConPassword]
sv_hostname "$[HostName]"
sets sv_projectName "$[HostName]" sets sv_projectDesc "$[HostName]"
# nested configs! #exec server_internal.cfg
# loading a server icon (96x96 PNG file) #load_server_icon myLogo.png
# convars for use from script set temp_convar "hey world!"
# disable announcing? clear out the master by uncommenting this #sv_master1 ""
# want to only allow players authenticated with a third-party provider like Steam? #sv_authMaxVariance 1 #sv_authMinTrust 5
# add system admins add_ace group.admin command allow # allow all commands add_ace group.admin command.quit deny # but don't allow quit
# hide player endpoints in external log output sv_endpointprivacy true
# server slots limit (default to 30) sv_maxclients $[Service.Slots]
# disable gui set svgui_disable true
sv_licenseKey ![LicenseKey]

#Download 7zip if needed
if not File.Exists(_7zaexe) : Script.WriteToConsole("Downloading 7zip...") wc = WebClient() wc.DownloadFile(_7zaurl, _7zazip); c=CompressionTools() c.Decompress(_7zazip, _7zapath) File.Delete(_7zazip)
